'''瓦德漢學院'''（'''Wadham College'''） 是[[英國|英國]][[牛津大學學院|牛津大學學院]]之一，位於[[牛津|牛津]]中部[[公園路|公園路]]南端，其名稱是爲了紀念[[詹姆斯一世_(英格蘭)|詹姆斯一世]]時[[薩默塞特郡|薩默塞特郡]]的地主[[多蘿西·瓦德漢|多蘿西·瓦德漢]]和[[尼古拉斯·瓦德漢|尼古拉斯·瓦德漢]]。

瓦德漢學院學風自由，以廣出左翼政治家和豐富的學生社團而聞名。<ref>[http://www.wadham.ox.ac.uk/about-wadham/wardens-welcome.html About Wadham] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wadham.ox.ac.uk/about-wadham/wardens-welcome.html |date=20191109171248 }}. Wadham.ox.ac.uk. Retrieved on 2013-09-23.</ref><ref>{{cite book | author = [[Alister_E._McGrath|Alister E. McGrath]] | title = [[A_Scientific_Theology|A Scientific Theology]] | volume = 1: Nature | chapter = Preface | page = xiii | chapter-url = http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ZyLhKnPWOjEC&pg=PR13&dq=wadham+college+left-wing&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&f=false | access-date = 2013-10-11 | archive-date = 2019-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191114130544/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=ZyLhKnPWOjEC&pg=PR13&dq=wadham+college+left-wing&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref> 2009年收到財政捐款6600萬英鎊，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.btinternet.com/~akme/OXCpress.html|title=Oxford College Endowment Incomes, 1973–2006|archiveurl=http://archive.is/Acra|archivedate=27 May 2012}} (updated July 2007){{dead link|date=November 2012|bot=Legobot}}</ref> 2011/2012學年在[[諾靈頓排名|諾靈頓排名]]上排在第4位。<ref name="classifications1">{{cite web |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/about_the_university/facts_and_figures/norringtontable.html#acollege_undergraduate_degree_classifications_201112_sorted_by_rank |title=Undergraduate Degree Classifications 2011/2012 – University of Oxford |first= |last= |work=ox.ac.uk |date=2012-08-12 |accessdate=23 August 2012 |archive-date=2014-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218014636/http://www.ox.ac.uk/about_the_university/facts_and_figures/norringtontable.html#acollege_undergraduate_degree_classifications_201112_sorted_by_rank |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 歷史==
該學院由多蘿西·瓦德漢成立於1610年，<ref name="History of Wadham">{{cite web|url=http://www.wadham.ox.ac.uk/about-wadham/history-of-wadham/history-of-wadham-2.html|title=History of Wadham|publisher=www.wadham.ox.ac.uk|accessdate=11 September 2009|last=|first=|archive-date=2019-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116174430/https://www.wadham.ox.ac.uk/about-wadham/history-of-wadham/history-of-wadham-2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 資金則來自于其亡夫尼古拉斯·瓦德漢（死於1609年），後來這一建造計劃還得到了皇室和教會的支持，并任命[[威廉·阿諾德_(建築師)|威廉·阿諾德]]為建築師，雖然多蘿西從沒有親自去過牛津，但直到1618年去世她都掌握著對學院的控制權。
[[Image:Nicholasanddoothywadham.jpg|250px]]

學院成立伊始便禁止所有女性進入該學院，唯一的例外是一位“年齡、地位和名譽都不會受到質疑”的洗衣婦。<ref name="History of Wadham"/> 這一傳統保持了數個世紀，1974年成為最早接受女性學員的學院之一。<ref name="Women_at_Oxford">{{cite web |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/about_the_university/introducing_oxford/women_at_oxford/ |title=Women at Oxford |publisher=[[University_of_Oxford|University of Oxford]] |accessdate=17 May 2013 |archive-date=2014-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218114957/http://www.ox.ac.uk/about_the_university/introducing_oxford/women_at_oxford/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===現代===

該學院也因強烈支持同性戀而出名，還有年度晚會“Queerfest”。這一傳統可追溯到18世紀該學院的一位同性戀院長（warden）[[Robert_Thistlethwayte|Robert Thistlethwayte]]，他因同性戀醜聞而不得不在1739年逃離英格蘭。<ref>{{cite book|url= http://books.google.com/books?id=lor1NiZNQ0gC&pg=PA351&lpg=PA351&dq=there-was-once-a-warden-of-wadham|title= Online excerpt from Thomas Dormandy's ''The Worst of Two Evils: The Fight Against Pain''|isbn= 9780300113228|author1= Dormandy|first1= Thomas|year= 2006|access-date= 2013-10-11|archive-date= 2014-01-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140111082648/http://books.google.com/books?id=lor1NiZNQ0gC&pg=PA351&lpg=PA351&dq=there-was-once-a-warden-of-wadham|dead-url= no}}</ref>

